{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Support us by Wishlisting</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/add_to_wishlist.gif?t=1708977933\" /><br>Hello I am Brian and this is my first publicly released game, thanks for checking it out!<br><strong>Kitsune Battlemage</strong> is an intense elemental magic combat game where you're not limited to any specific school or style of magic. Choose your abilities and wage battle using powerful combinations of elemental spells! <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/earthbomb_backflip_trimmed_banner.gif?t=1708977933\" /><br><br><strong>Choose</strong> abilities from any of the elements and switch things up to engage in tactical spellcasting battles.<br> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/dvno_wallrun_trimmed_banner.gif?t=1708977933\" /><br><br><strong>Battlemages</strong> enter the training grounds via portals that connect worlds. Train your skills against others in elemental combat!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/alo_movement_trimmed_banner.gif?t=1708977933\" /><br><br><strong>Master </strong>the elements: Fire, Frost, and Earth. Choose your abilities to match your playstyle, fit your team, and battle your opponents!<br><br><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Online arena combat<br></li><li>Offline horde mode<br></li><li>Choose any combination of Fire, Earth, and Ice magic<br></li><li>Health, mana, and stamina resources that can be attacked via different skills<br></li><li>Primary attacks have stacking buffs and debuffs</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"It's not a cult!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1851840/db3d4181ea66e74f8e6d42ad91c598a1b